long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Send current page URL to a web application's form of your choice. Only when you choose to (click add on's button in the tool bar). 

Handler for youtube now, but later will have for other sites. Handler logs what action taken.

For other pages, adds to log file. 


Can customize the URL, the primary parameter to send to the handler and the log location.

Default handler will log all calls.
